Help

I'm vegan / shop sustainably / fat / thin / old / young / pregnant / a goth / passionately opposed to all things velour, can you help?
One word: yes. Just let Adla know about your specific needs when you fill out the quiz and she can cater to them. Whoever you are, you're all rad to Adla.

I'm not sure I want to be told what to wear...
Good for you! You are the master of your own wardrobe. Everything Adla hunts down is based specifically on your personal profile and what you tell Adla. And you only try on what you want to. It's all about you, baby!

How quickly will I get my clothes?
You'll get your recommendations within 24 hours and you choose what you'd like to try on. Depending on the brand, we can deliver you the clothes from as early as next day. Some brands can take a couple more days.

How long do I have to try them on?
We'll give you 5 days and a personalised playlist to listen to whilst you try them on. Whether you're into ABBA Dancing Queen or electronic jazz flute, we don't discriminate.

How do I return the rejects?
Hit us up with a message and we'll pick them up in a convenient 30 min slot

How much does it cost?
You don't have to pay any money upfront. So if you can only afford one dress, but want to try three, you can! Mind. Blown. Adla will let you know how much each item costs from the start. Pay for the ones you want to keep AFTER you've tried them on. Isn't this how it should always be?!

How do I pay up?
If you've decided you want to keep something, Adla will ping you a link to make a payment. Adla accepts Visa, MasterCard, American Express, JCB, Discover, and Diners Club. All payments are secured by Stripe.

Can I use Adla wherever I live?
Sadly, she's only in London and the Bay Area, California at the moment. But hit her up on Instagram @Adla.site if you'd like her to come to your hood.

Does my butt look too big in this?
No. Always, no.

Why are my brand new white shirts the ones I always get sauce on?
Because it's a cruel world.

Is anyone still reading this?
I don't know. Are you?

) }
